<div class="tip-card">🖱️ <strong>How the upgrade items are applied:</strong> the local item docs describe both backpack upgrades as <strong>drag-and-click</strong> upgrades on the backpack worn in the <strong>accessory slot</strong>. First apply the Big Backpack Upgrade to the Leather Backpack there, then apply the Ancient Metal Backpack Upgrade the same way. The same local backpack doc also suggests that the leather and ancient-metal states in this route are <strong>not intended to be removed</strong> from that slot.</div>

<h3>Advanced Storage</h3>
<p>Based on the local item-info, v0.9.0 simplifies chest and barrel progression into the <strong>dedicated upgrade-item</strong> route. These upgrades require the <strong>Ancient Metal Container Knowledge Book</strong> and are used on already placed storage blocks.</p>
<table class="compare-table">
