<h2 id="knowledge-books-en">Knowledge Books</h2>
<p>A Knowledge Book is a special item that unlocks advanced recipes. If a recipe is gated behind a Knowledge Book, you <strong>cannot craft it</strong> even if you have all the materials!</p>
<div class="warning-box">🔒 <strong>Hard requirement:</strong> Based on current v0.9.0 observations and item pages, reliably confirmed Knowledge Book sources include <strong>treasure chests in underground dungeons</strong> and <strong>surface Pillager Fortress chests</strong>.</div>

